# MegaPy TODO

## Completed
- [x] Thumbnail/Preview upload - Fixed URL endpoint bug (was always /0, now uses /{attr_type})
- [x] MediaProcessor - Added is_media(), is_image(), is_video(), process() methods
- [x] MediaResult dataclass for thumbnail/preview processing results
- [x] Unit tests for MediaProcessor, ThumbnailService, PreviewService (54 tests)
- [x] Unit tests for file attribute upload (URL endpoints, encryption, format)
- [x] Video/Media Attributes (type 8*/9*) - Auto-extraction and upload via pfa command
- [x] MediaProcessor.extract_metadata() - Improved to detect shortformat (MP4/H.264/AAC)
- [x] Documentation for video attributes in docs/video_attributes.md
- [x] Unit tests for video attributes upload (25 tests)

## Future Improvements
